			<!-- icon and title -->
			<div class="smallfont">
				
				<strong>New Idea: Chill and Burn counters</strong>
			</div>
			<hr size="1" color="" />
			<!-- / icon and title -->
		
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div>In EQ today we have PC and NPC spells that increase/decrease Poison, Disease and Curse counters. <br />
<br />
I was thinking this would be an excellent time to introduce Chill and Burn counters and make druids masters of alleviating and causing chill and burn. Some spell ideas that uses these new counters include :-<br />
<br />
Decrease chill counter spell line - Alleviate Chill, Alleviate Frost, Alleviate Frostbite, etc..<br />
Decrease burn counter spell line - Alleviate Burn, Alleviate Fire, Alleviate Wildfire, etc..<br />
<br />
Immolation &amp; Ro spell lines - Add Increase burn counter<br />
Eci line - Add Increase chill counter</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
	
	</td>
</tr>
